INSERT INTO texts VALUES(11511036,'Elegantea Kingdom','Each time an effect resolves that changed the Level of an "Elegantea" monster(s) other than this card put 1 E-Counter on this card. Once per turn: You can remove 1 E-Counter from this card to increase/decrease the Level of an "Elegantea" monster you control by 1. If this card would be destroyed by a card effect you can remove 2 E-Counters instead. If an "Elegantea" Xyz Monster''s effect you control requires detaching an Xyz Material as a cost, you can remove 3 E-Counters from this card instead.','Select monster to incease level by 1','Remove 3  Elegantea Counters instead?',' ','','','','','','','','','','','',' ','');
