INSERT INTO texts VALUES(11511048,'Art of Anchient Witchery','Reveal 1 "Elegantea" monster in your Hand to target 1 Spell/Trap Card on the field, destroy it, your opponent cannot activate that card in response to this card''s effect. If you control 2 "Elegantea" Xyz Monsters with the same Rank but different names, you can banish this card from your Graveyard; destroy all face down cards your opponent controls.','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',' ','');
INSERT INTO texts VALUES(11511049,'Warrior''s Fury','Activate only when an "Elegantea" monster you control destroys an opponent monster by battle and sends it to Graveyard, it can make a second attack on an opponent monster, also if it is in Defense Position; inflict piercing damage to your opponent life points.','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',' ','');
INSERT INTO texts VALUES(11511050,'Warrior''s Invincible Will','Active only when your opponent Special Summons a monster, Special Summon 2 Level 4 or lower "Elegantea" monsters from your Graveyard.','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',' ','');
INSERT INTO texts VALUES(11511051,'Elegantea Successor','Activate only when an "Elegantea" monster you control whose Level is different from its original Level is destroyed and send to Graveyard, target 1 "Elegantea" monster you control and increase its Level with that difference.','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',' ','');
INSERT INTO texts VALUES(11511052,'Elegantea Curse','Activate only when an opponent monster declares an attack on an "Elegantea" monster you control, negate the attack, also your opponent monsters cannot attack that monster for the rest of this turn unless it''s the only monster you control. After that Set this card face-down again instead of sending it to the Graveyard.','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',' ','');
INSERT INTO texts VALUES(11511053,'Elegantea Barrier','Activate only when your opponent activates a Spell Card, Trap Card or monster''s effect while you control an "Elegantea" monster, negate the activation and destroy it. If you control an "Elegantea" Xyz Monster, you can Set this card face-down from your Graveyard, but banishes it when it leaves the field.','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',' ','');
INSERT INTO texts VALUES(11511054,'Warrior''s Rage','When a monster(s) would be Special Summoned, while you have an "Elegantea" Xyz Monster(s) in your Graveyard, negate the Summon and destroy it then Special Summon 1 "Elegantea" Xyz Monster from your Graveyard and attach this card to it as an Xyz Material.','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',' ','');
INSERT INTO texts VALUES(11511055,'Warrior''s Last Will','Activate only when an "Elegantea" monster you control is destroyed by battle by your opponent attacking monster and sent to Graveyard, target 1 "Elegantea" Xyz Monster you control, Special Summon 1 "Elegantea" Xyz Monster from your Extra Deck with 1 Rank higher than the targeted monster using it as an Xyz Material (this Summon is treated as an Xyz Summon, Xyz Materials attached to the target are also attached to it).','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',' ','');
INSERT INTO texts VALUES(11511056,'Elegantea Angel Kyle',replace(replace('2 Level 3 "Elegantea" monsters\r\nOnce per turn: You can Roll a six-sided die, add 1 "Elegantea" monster from your Deck to your Hand with a Level equal to the Roll.Once per turn: You can detach 1 material from this card, then target 1 Xyz Monster you control, Special Summon 1 "Elegantea" monster that is 1 Rank higher than that target as the Xyz Material. (This Special Summon is treated as an Xyz Summon. Xyz Materials attached to that target also become Xyz Materials on the Summoned monster.)','\r',char(13)),'\n',char(10)),'Add 1 "Elegantea" monster to Hand','Special Summon 1 Xyz "Elegantea" monster','','','','','','','','','','','','',' ','');
INSERT INTO texts VALUES(11511101,'Fury-Horned Tiger','You can Normal Summon 1 Level 4 or lower "Horned Dragon" monster in addition to your Normal Summon or set (You can only gain this effect once per turn). If this card is sent to Graveyard you can Special Summon 1 "Horned Tiger" from your Deck except "Fury-Horned Tiger".','Normal Summon (Fury-Horned Tiger)','','','','','','','','','','','','','',' ','');
INSERT INTO texts VALUES(11511102,'Stone-Horned Tiger','During the Damage Step, if a "Tri-Horned Dragon" you control battles an opponent monster you discard this card from your Hand, it gains 1350 ATK (permanently), also it cannot be destroyed by battle this turn. When your opponent activates a card effect that would targets "Horned" card(s) in your Spell/Trap Zone you can discard this card from your Hand to negate that card''s effect and destroy it.','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',' ','');
INSERT INTO texts VALUES(11511103,'Wind-Horned Tiger','You can target 1 "Horned" monster you control, return it to your Hand then Special Summon 1 "Horned" monster from your Deck with the same Level as the returned card but with a different Type. If this card is sent to Graveyard, you can Special Summon 1 "Tri-Horned Dragon" monster form your Graveyard. You can only use each of "Wind-Horned Tiger" effects once per turn.','','','','','','','','','','','','','','',' ','');
INSERT INTO texts VALUES(11511104,'Wind-Horned Dragon','You can Normal Summon 1 Level 4 or lower "Horned Tiger" monster in addition to your Normal Summon or set(You can only gain this effect once per turn). If this card is sent to Graveyard you can add 1 "Horned Dragon" from your Deck to your Hand except "Wind-Horned Dragon".','Normal Summon (Wind-Horned Dragon)','','','','','','','','','','','','','',' ','');
INSERT INTO texts VALUES(11511105,'Bi-Horned Dragon',replace('[ Pendulum Effect ]\n"Tri-Horned Dragon" monsters you control cannot be targeted or destroyed by your opponent card effects. If you control "Horned Tiger" monster(s) face up on your side of the field you can add 1 "Tri-Horned Dragon" from your Deck to Hand. You can only use this effect once per turn. You can only Pendulum Summon "Horned" monsters.\n----------------------------------------\n[ Monster Effect ]\nThis card gains 100 ATK for each "Horned" monster you control. If this card is sent to Graveyard you can add 1 "Horned Tiger" monster from Deck to Hand. You can only use this effect of "Bi-Horned Dragon" once per turn.','\n',char(10)),'','','','','','','','','','','','','','',' ','');
INSERT INTO texts VALUES(11511106,'Uni-Horned Dragon',replace('[ Pendulum Effect ]\n"Tri-Horned Dragon" monsters you control cannot be destroyed by battle. If you control "Horned Tiger" monster(s) face up on your side of the field, this card''s Pendulum Scale becomes 3. You can only Pendulum Summon "Horned" monsters.\n----------------------------------------\n[ Monster Effect ]\nThis card gains 100 ATK for each "Horned" monster you control. If this card is sent to Graveyard you can add 1 "Horned Tiger" monster from Graveyard to Hand. You can only use this effect of "Uni-Horned Dragon" once per turn.','\n',char(10)),'','','','','','','','','','','','','','',' ','');
